description:
This week on Unqualified, Anna and Sim sit down with Hollywood legend, Sharon Stone (Casino, Basic Instinct)! The gang talks about unconventional beauty, what is "sexy," first date etiquette and Sharon takes down the infamous Karen Sarducci! After the break, they call Charlene, whose perfect boyfriend has a low sex drive, and Lauren, whose life was changed by Sharon's advice for her.
